				<td rowspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" style="text-align: justify;" width="100%" valign=top>
				<DIV></DIV>
<P>The mark of the spirits quest is a solo task, meaning the kill element does not update for the entire group in the way a shared task would.&nbsp; To get kill credit for each spirit, your character has to receive XP for the spirit's death.&nbsp; If you don't get XP (because you're in a raid, or because you're out of range, or any of the other&nbsp;reasons you would not get XP for a kill) you won't get kill credit in the task window.&nbsp;&nbsp;</P>
<P>I hope this information was helpful.&nbsp; If you're receiving XP messages and still not getting kill credit, please let me know and I'll look into it further.</P>
<P>Thanks,</P>
<P>Osrhan</P>
				
